{{!
    @template block_workload/modal_iframe

    Iframe body of the manage-page modals; rendered client-side by the
    block_workload/manage AMD module (initList).

    Context variables required for this template:
    * url - iframe source URL
    * title - accessible name of the iframe (the modal title)

    @package   block_workload
    @copyright 2026 Yurii Lysak
    @license   http://www.gnu.org/copyleft/gpl.html GNU GPL v3 or later

    Example context (json):
    {
        "url": "http://example.com/blocks/workload/manage.php?action=add&modal=1",
        "title": "Add cohort"
    }
}}
<iframe src="{{url}}" title="{{title}}"
        style="width:100%;min-height:160px;border:none;display:block;"></iframe>
